aggregate: function aggregate(tuple(address target, bytes callData)[] calls) payable returns (uint256 blockNumber, bytes[] returnData)

blockAndAggregate: function blockAndAggregate(tuple(address target, bytes callData)[] calls) payable returns (uint256 blockNumber, bytes32 blockHash, tuple(bool success, bytes returnData)[] returnData)

getEthBalance: function getEthBalance(address addr) view returns (uint256 balance)
